        <Parent_String>shaping and guiding tools [300162806], shaping and guiding equipment [300024808], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
